text:
──Sorry, Producer!
Sorry to keep you waiting...!

No, it's okay.
You had contacted me.

You were a bit later than expected...
Did you find what you lost?

I found it!
But... it took more time than I thought.

No, no, it's good to help someone in trouble.
This wasn't urgent anyway.

Just, if it looks like you're going to be late,
please chain another message or call me.

Ah...! You're right...!
I'm really sorry!!

I was just thinking, "I need to hurry!"
and focusing only on that...
